{"lemma":"عُقْدَةٌ","slug":"عُقْدَةٌ","root":"ع.ق.د","root_slug":"ع-ق-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ق-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عُقْدَة","root":"عقد","pos":"N","occurrence_count":4},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n29880"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8F%D9%82%D9%92%D8%AF%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"knot","examples":[{"text":"وَمِنْ شَرِّ النَّفَّاثَاتِ فِي الْعُقَدِ"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"knot, nautical mile"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"complex (set of deep-rooted emotions that negatively influence one)"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʕuq.da/","/ʕuɡ.da/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n29880","headword_ar":"عُقْدَةٌ","root":"Eqd","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A knot; a tie;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, Msb;) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuqadN","text_ar":"عُقَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) [Hence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~af~aAvaAtu fiY AlEuqadi","text_ar":"النَّفَّاثَاتُ فِى العُقَدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nfv","text_ar":"نفث"},{"kind":"text","text":". And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEuqodapu","text_ar":"العُقْدَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The star a Piscium;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as being in the place of the knot of the two strings: the same, app., that is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxayoTayoni","text_ar":"الخَيْطَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaqodu","text_ar":"عَقْدُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", mentioned by Freytag under"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiqodN","text_ar":"عِقْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". Hence also] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHl~lt Euqaduhu","text_ar":"تحلّلت عُقَدُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His knots became loosed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"untied"},{"kind":"text","text":"], meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his anger became appeased."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Euqodatihi DaEofN","text_ar":"فِى عُقْدَتِهِ ضَعْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In his judgment and his consideration of his own affairs is a weakness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSiyfu AlEuqodapi","text_ar":"حَصِيفُ العُقْدَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", occurring in a letter of 'Omar, means (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Firm"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in judgment, and in the management, conducting, ordering,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regulating, of affairs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HSf","text_ar":"حصف"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY lisaAnihi EuqodapN","text_ar":"فِى لِسَانِهِ عُقْدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, L, K *) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In his tongue is an impediment"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as though it were tied"},{"kind":"text","text":"], or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a distortion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L. [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaqida","text_ar":"عَقِدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"knot, tie,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bond,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L,) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obligation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K,) of marriage, (O, L, K,) and of anything, (O, K,) as a sale and the like: (TA:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ratification"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, L, Msb) of marriage (O, Msb) &c., (Msb,) or of anything. (L.) It is said in a trad. relating to prayer,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laka mino quluwbinaA Euqodapu Aln~adami","text_ar":"لَكَ مِنْ قُلُوبِنَا عُقْدَةُ النَّدَمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning [We offer"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to Thee, from our hearts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the ratification of the resolution to repent."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A promise of obedience,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vow of allegiance, ratified to persons in acknowlegment of their being prefects,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"governors:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, L, K, * TA:) from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euqodapu AlHaboli","text_ar":"عُقْدَةُ الحَبْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the knot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tie, of the cord"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rope"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (O:) thus in the saying, in a trad. of Ubeí,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"halaka A^aholu AlEuqodapi","text_ar":"هَلَكَ اَهْلُ العُقْدَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Those who have received the promise of obedience"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have perished;"},{"kind":"text","text":"virtually meaning the same as the saying in the sentence here following]. (L.) And [hence also] The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prefecture over,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"government of, a town, country, province,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuqadN","text_ar":"عُقَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L, K, TA:) thus in the saying of 'Omar,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"halaka A^aholu AlEuqadi","text_ar":"هَلَكَ اَهْلُ العُقَدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The possessors of the prefectures"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have perished"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L.) ―         -b4-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place where a knot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"node, is formed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [particularly]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an uneven juncture"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EavomN","text_ar":"عَثْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":") [of a bone] in the arm: (S, O, K:) thus in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jubirato yaduhu","text_ar":"جُبِرَتْ يَدُهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY EuqodapK","text_ar":"عَلَى عُقْدَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His arm was set and joined unevenly, so that a node,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"protuberance, was produced in the bone"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, O:) and in like manner one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabara EaZomahu EalaY EuqodapK","text_ar":"جَبَرَ عَظْمَهُ عَلَى عُقْدَةٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He set and joined his bone unevenly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b5-  [Hence also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A joint,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an articulation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the fingers: and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a bone"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a finger, i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any one of the phalanges:"},{"kind":"text","text":"it is used in both of these senses in the present day: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEuqodapu mina AlA^aSaAbiEi","text_ar":"العُقْدَةُ مِنَ الاَصَابِعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in the Msb, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nml","text_ar":"نمل"},{"kind":"text","text":", in explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^anomalapu","text_ar":"الاَنْمَلَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; which is generally expl. as meaning “ the head of the finger, ” or “ the portion in which is the nail. ” (See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEoqidN","text_ar":"مَعْقِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A knot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"joint,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a cane and the like. And what is termed"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A knot"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the horn of a mountain-goat (as in the S and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hyd","text_ar":"حيد"},{"kind":"text","text":") and the like. ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A knot"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a tree. ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A node,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a plant,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whence a leaf shoots forth: a bud,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gem,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a plant: and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any fruit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"produce,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a plant,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forming a compact and roundish head;"},{"kind":"text","text":"by some termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HasakapN","text_ar":"حَسَكَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", n. un. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HasakN","text_ar":"حَسَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEuqodataAni","text_ar":"العُقْدَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The nodes of a planet."},{"kind":"text","text":"(See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tin~aynN","text_ar":"تِنَّينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b10-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuqodapN","text_ar":"عُقْدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Any small nodous lump; such as the substance of a ganglion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gud~apN","text_ar":"غُدَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gland,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"glandular body;"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gunodubapN","text_ar":"غُنْدُبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A knob"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a general sense. ―         -b11-  And hence,] The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"penis"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a dog (IAar, A, O, L, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compressus in coitu, et extremitate turgens:"},{"kind":"text","text":"otherwise it is not thus called: (IAar, O, L:) and when this is the case, the epithet ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoqadu","text_ar":"اَعْقَدُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to the dog. (IAar, O.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An estate consisting of land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of land and a house,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a house"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land yielding a revenue,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a house and palm-trees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DayoEapN","text_ar":"ضَيْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, O, L, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaqaArN","text_ar":"عَقَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which a person has acquired"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiEotaqadahu","text_ar":"اِعْتَقَدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as a possession."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, L, K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Any land abounding with herbage"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and with trees."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place abounding with trees"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"palm-trees;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with trees and palm-trees;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, L, K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with trees of the kinds called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rimov","text_ar":"رِمْث"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Earofaj","text_ar":"عَرْفَج"},{"kind":"text","text":", or, accord. to some,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not of the latter kind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"serving for pasturage:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a garden of many palm-trees, surrounded by a wall:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a town,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"village, abounding with palm-trees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"the crows of which are not made to fly away: (Ibn-Habeeb, L:) [whence] it is said in a prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=lafu mino guraAbi EuqodapK","text_ar":"ا=لَفُ مِنْ غُرَابِ عُقْدَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"More familiar than the crow of a place abounding with trees"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"palm-trees"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; because its crow is not made to fly away, (S, O, L, K, [or, as in some copies of the S and K, does not fly away,]) on account of the abundance of its trees; (K;) [or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino guraAbi Euqodapa","text_ar":"مِنْ غُرَابِ عُقْدَةَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"than the crow of ' Okdeh;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euqodap","text_ar":"عُقْدَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is perfectly decl. as a name for any fruitful land, and is imperfectly decl. as a proper name of a particular land (O, K) abounding with palmtrees. (O.) Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasturage, sufficient for camels:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place abounding with herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasturage, sufficient for cattle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pasturage such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janobap","text_ar":"جَنْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, L, K, [in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janabap","text_ar":"جَنَبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", and in my MS. copy of the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junobap","text_ar":"جُنْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":",])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remaining from the next preceding year;"},{"kind":"text","text":"also termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurowapN","text_ar":"عُرْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O, L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remains of pasturage:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuqadN","text_ar":"عُقَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, L) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiqaAdN","text_ar":"عِقَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) And accord. to the copies of the K, it signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Camels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cattle, that are constrained to feed upon trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but [this is evidently a mistake; for] it is said in the L, [as also in the O,] sometimes camels, or cattle, are constrained to feed upon trees, and these ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trees"},{"kind":"text","text":"] are termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euqodap","text_ar":"عُقْدَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eurowap","text_ar":"عُرْوَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but while the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janobap","text_ar":"جَنْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"exists, the trees are not termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euqodap","text_ar":"عُقْدَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"nor"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eurowap","text_ar":"عُرْوَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Anything whereby a man feels himself to be well established, and whereon he relies;"},{"kind":"text","text":"from the same word signifying “ a garden of many palmtrees, surrounded by a wall; ” because, when a man has this, he considers his condition to be well established: (L, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an estate consisting of land"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of land and a house"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaqaArN","text_ar":"عَقَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which is a sufficiency for a man:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuqadN","text_ar":"عُقَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiqodN","text_ar":"عِقْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["L","O","K","TA","Msb","S","IAar","A"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}